The [libbitcoin-server](https://github.com/libbitcoin/libbitcoin-server) library extends [[libbitcoin-node|Libbitcoin_Node]] with a blockchain query service based on [ZeroMQ](http://zeromq.org). The first version was called [[Obelisk]].

##Console Application
The library is accompanied by the console application [[Bitcoin Server|Bitcoin_Server]] (bs).

##Dependencies

* [boost](http://www.boost.org)
* [secp256k1](https://github.com/bitcoin/secp256k1)
* [[libbitcoin|Libbitcoin_Common]]
* [[libbitcoin-consensus (optional)|Libbitcoin_Consensus]]
* [[libbitcoin-blockchain|Libbitcoin_Blockchain]]
* [[libbitcoin-node|Libbitcoin_Node]]

